
***** 'SetColorMaterial' command *****

token(s):
T_SetColorMaterial SetColorMaterial

rule(s):
commande <-- VAR_SURFACE '.' T_SetColorMaterial '(' expr ')'

parameters:
1. VAR_SURFACE
2. expr: boolean


Description:
Enable/Disable color material for the input surface,
if param 2>0.5, enable color material, otherwise, disable it.
Color material allows to see the RGB colors of each vertex, but also
disables the transparency of the surface.



